data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in a peaceful, friendly neighborhood. This home offers open living room, eat in kitchen, perfect for entertaining family and friends. A split plan with a roomy master suite that includes a relaxing jacuzzi tub, walk in shower, and large closet space. It also has hardwood flooring, plush carpet, spacious laundry room, a full second bathroom to accommodate the additional bedrooms. A very nice backyard with a covered patio and privacy fence perfect for your next family cookout. This home is conveniently located to everything in the downtown Little Rock area. This property is AS IS and a MUST SEE!
